--- General / OS / Editor Files ---
Ignore OS-generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

Ignore editor-specific settings
.vscode/
.idea/

--- Frontend (React + Vite) ---
Ignore all node_modules directories
frontend/node_modules/

Ignore build output folder
frontend/dist/

Ignore environment variables. These are secret and should not be committed.
Only commit .env.example if you have one.
frontend/.env
frontend/.env.local
frontend/.env.*.local

Ignore logs
frontend/npm-debug.log*
frontend/yarn-debug.log*
frontend/yarn-error.log*

--- Backend (Python + FastAPI) ---
Ignore Python virtual environments
backend/venv/
backend/env/
backend/.venv/

Ignore Python bytecode and cache
backend/pycache/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

Ignore backend environment variables
backend/.env

Ignore user-uploaded files. The 'uploads' directory should not be tracked.
backend/uploads/